  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >🏠 Welcome to The Silent Forests! 🌳</h2><br><u><strong>🎮 Game Overview:</strong></u><br>Embark on a spellbinding odyssey across diverse realms in this immersive adventure! Dive into the mysterious Silent Forests, navigate perilous sewers, escape an enigmatic house, and unravel concealed truths in a breathtaking finale. Brace yourself for a journey teeming with puzzles, formidable monsters, and unexpected twists! 🚀<br><br><u><strong>🌲 Silent Forests</strong></u><br>Pursue your elusive home through the enchanting Silent Forests. Solve intricate puzzles, gather mystical books, and confront the mysterious monsters lurking in the shoadows in an adrenaline-pumping chase! 📚🌲<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2822080/extras/5ac0e621a13c4ea3f504cfbd3f5f57b3.poster.avif?t=1746126390\" width=616 height=252 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2822080/extras/5ac0e621a13c4ea3f504cfbd3f5f57b3.webm?t=1746126390\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2822080/extras/5ac0e621a13c4ea3f504cfbd3f5f57b3.mp4?t=1746126390\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><u><strong>🕳️ Sewer Secrets</strong></u><br>Descend into the depths of mysterious sewers, surmount challenging puzzles, and outmaneuver the menacing monsters.🚪🔍<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2822080/extras/71cd00649cc0b58566ae65ce9e5556bb.poster.avif?t=1746126390\" width=616 height=252 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2822080/extras/71cd00649cc0b58566ae65ce9e5556bb.webm?t=1746126390\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2822080/extras/71cd00649cc0b58566ae65ce9e5556bb.mp4?t=1746126390\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><u><strong>🏡 Haunted House</strong></u><br>Navigate through a peculiar house, finish your objectives, and execute a swift escape! 🚗💨<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2822080/extras/39b2ff0a2066152340470ed509c09a12.poster.avif?t=1746126390\" width=616 height=252 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2822080/extras/39b2ff0a2066152340470ed509c09a12.webm?t=1746126390\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2822080/extras/39b2ff0a2066152340470ed509c09a12.mp4?t=1746126390\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong><u>🎮 Dive into a World of Enigmatic Challenges! 🧩</u></strong><br>🔐 Manipulate <strong>levers</strong>, crack <strong>keypads</strong>, balance on <strong>weight sensors</strong>, and swipe <strong>keycards</strong>.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2822080/extras/15d53206609e1d52fedcadfb2513295c.poster.avif?t=1746126390\" width=616 height=252 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2822080/extras/15d53206609e1d52fedcadfb2513295c.webm?t=1746126390\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2822080/extras/15d53206609e1d52fedcadfb2513295c.mp4?t=1746126390\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><u><strong>🎭 Wacky Narrator</strong></u><br>Experience an uproarious narrator guiding you through humor, spine-chilling encounters, and an adventure bursting with excitement! 🎙️😂👻<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2822080/extras/f48f6cce25890315e4b0a8f2faade599.poster.avif?t=1746126390\" width=616 height=252 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2822080/extras/f48f6cce25890315e4b0a8f2faade599.webm?t=1746126390\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2822080/extras/f48f6cce25890315e4b0a8f2faade599.mp4?t=1746126390\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br><u><strong>🌟 Key Features:</strong></u><br><br>✨ Gripping narrative with unpredictable twists!<br>🧩 Intricate puzzles and mind-bending mysteries.<br>👾 Heart-racing encounters with formidable monsters.<br>🏃 Reflex-testing escape sequences.<br>🔍 Uncover concealed truths in a climactic conclusion.<br>😂 Engaging narrator with a mix of humor, scares, and exhilaration!<br><br>Get ready for an unparalleled adventure filled with jaw-dropping surprises, laughter, and spine-tingling moments. Your extraordinary journey begins now! 🌟🗝️🚪<br><br><u><strong>✨ Show Your Support! Wishlist and Follow! ✨</strong></u><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2822080/extras/2dc7e7cbf2147ddf6f1c8d86110efaaa.poster.avif?t=1746126390\" width=620 height=60 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2822080/extras/2dc7e7cbf2147ddf6f1c8d86110efaaa.webm?t=1746126390\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2822080/extras/2dc7e7cbf2147ddf6f1c8d86110efaaa.mp4?t=1746126390\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
  "about_the_game": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >🏠 Welcome to The Silent Forests! 🌳</h2><br><u><strong>🎮 Game Overview:</strong></u><br>Embark on a spellbinding odyssey across diverse realms in this immersive adventure! Dive into the mysterious Silent Forests, navigate perilous sewers, escape an enigmatic house, and unravel concealed truths in a breathtaking finale. Brace yourself for a journey teeming with puzzles, formidable monsters, and unexpected twists! 🚀<br><br><u><strong>🌲 Silent Forests</strong></u><br>Pursue your elusive home through the enchanting Silent Forests. Solve intricate puzzles, gather mystical books, and confront the mysterious monsters lurking in the shoadows in an adrenaline-pumping chase! 📚🌲<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2822080/extras/5ac0e621a13c4ea3f504cfbd3f5f57b3.poster.avif?t=1746126390\" width=616 height=252 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2822080/extras/5ac0e621a13c4ea3f504cfbd3f5f57b3.webm?t=1746126390\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2822080/extras/5ac0e621a13c4ea3f504cfbd3f5f57b3.mp4?t=1746126390\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><u><strong>🕳️ Sewer Secrets</strong></u><br>Descend into the depths of mysterious sewers, surmount challenging puzzles, and outmaneuver the menacing monsters.🚪🔍<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2822080/extras/71cd00649cc0b58566ae65ce9e5556bb.poster.avif?t=1746126390\" width=616 height=252 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2822080/extras/71cd00649cc0b58566ae65ce9e5556bb.webm?t=1746126390\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steams